sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant vLLM as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC / HF Hub)
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA VRAM

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup
        vLLM->>Storage: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: IAM / ServiceAccount / Bearer
        Storage-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
        vLLM->>GPU: Load model to VRAM<br/>CUDA memory transfer
        GPU-->>vLLM: Model ready
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
        Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>mTLS (Istio)
        Istio->>vLLM: HTTP request<br/>8000/TCP<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        vLLM->>GPU: Run inference<br/>CUDA
        GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
        vLLM-->>Istio: JSON response
        Istio-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response (HTTPS)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)
        Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerationService<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
        Gateway->>Istio: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033<br/>mTLS (Istio)
        Istio->>TGIS: gRPC request<br/>8033/TCP<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        TGIS->>vLLM: Translate to HTTP<br/>POST /v1/completions<br/>8000/TCP localhost
        vLLM->>GPU: Run inference<br/>CUDA
        GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
        vLLM-->>TGIS: HTTP response
        TGIS-->>Istio: gRPC response
        Istio-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
        Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response (HTTPS)
    end
